<p>Fortune.js is a library for managing data in Node.js and web browsers. It provides data querying and manipulation, business logic isolation, and external I/O, ensuring a baseline for interoperability and allowing implementations to be swapped interchangeably.</p>
<p>The latest version is <strong>{{version}}</strong>, get it from <code>npm</code>:</p>
